former white house aide oliver l north began 
using iranian armssale proceeds to arm nicaraguan rebels two months 
before he told congress the diversion had started irancontra 
prosecutors said friday 
a substantial quantity of weapons were bought for the contras 
in december 1985 from money left over from the aborted sale by 
