antennas and telescope mirrors 
also during the spacewalk chretien and volkov mounted outside 
mir a panel with samples of different materials and coatings 
after six months the panel is to be removed and taken back to 
earth for study of how the materials and coatings withstood sharp 
temperature fluctuations and solar radiation in space tass said 
the soviets have said they intend to build large structures in 
space for research and the techniques and materials the cosmonauts 
