judge who called him amoral not immoral 
david p bloom 24 whose swindle earned him the title wall 
street whiz kid pleaded guilty in march to one count each of mail 
fraud and securities fraud most of the investors he conned were 
friends of his parents prosecutors said 
i have betrayed my own sense of morality and values and 
